videos.comment:
Roses are red and violets are blue.
A note of the dead is right in your view.
A ghost on your bed you find out the rules.
Then go for the pen and write in your room.
The Tokyo feds end up finding the clues.
Don't know where you tread and in spite of your youth.
You're broken and dead for your crimes and induced.
